    "content": "<html>\n<head>\n    <title>Deque Example</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: monospace;\n        }\n        input[type=\"text\"] {\n            width: 50%;\n        }\n        input[type=\"number\"] {\n            width: 50%;\n        }\n        button {\n            padding: 5px 10px;\n            margin: 5px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        button:hover {\n            background-color: #ccc;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>Deque Example</h1>\n    <h2>Deque Basics</h2>\n    <p>A deque is a data structure that follows the LIFO (Last In First Out) principle.</p>\n    <p>Deque example: <button onclick=\"addDeque('deque')\">AddDeque</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"printDeque()\">PrintDeque</button>\n    <button onclick=\"removeDeque()\">RemoveDeque</button>\n    <button onclick=\"clearDeque()\">ClearDeque</button>\n    <h2>Deque Operations</h2>\n    <p>Insert at the front: <button onclick=\"insertAtFront('deque')\">InsertAtFront</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"insertAtFront('deque')\">InsertAtFront</button>\n    <button onclick=\"insertAtFront('deque')\">InsertAtFront</button>\n    <button onclick=\"insertAtFront('deque')\">InsertAtFront</button>\n    <h2>Insert at the back: <button onclick=\"insertAtBack('deque')\">InsertAtBack</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"insertAtBack('deque')\">InsertAtBack</button>\n    <button onclick=\"insertAtBack('deque')\">InsertAtBack</button>\n    <button onclick=\"insertAtBack('deque')\">InsertAtBack</button>\n    <h2>Remove from the front: <button onclick=\"removeFromFront()\">RemoveFromFront</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"removeFromFront()\">RemoveFromFront</button>\n    <button onclick=\"removeFromFront()\">RemoveFromFront</button>\n    <button onclick=\"removeFromFront()\">RemoveFromFront</button>\n    <h2>Remove from the back: <button onclick=\"removeFromBack()\">RemoveFromBack</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"removeFromBack()\">RemoveFromBack</button>\n    <button onclick=\"removeFromBack()\">RemoveFromBack</button>\n    <button onclick=\"removeFromBack()\">RemoveFromBack</button>\n    <h2>Clear Deque: <button onclick=\"clearDeque()\">ClearDeque</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"clearDeque()\">ClearDeque</button>\n    <h2>Print Deque: <button onclick=\"printDeque()\">PrintDeque</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"printDeque()\">PrintDeque</button>\n    <h2>Get Size: <button onclick=\"getSize()\">GetSize</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"getSize()\">GetSize</button>\n    <h2>Front Element: <button onclick=\"getFront()\">Front Element</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"getFront()\">Front Element</button>\n    <h2>Back Element: <button onclick=\"getBack()\">Back Element</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"getBack()\">Back Element</button>\n    <h2>Peek: <button onclick=\"peek()\">Peek</button></p>\n    <button onclick=\"peek()\">Peek</button>\n    <script>\n        let deque = new Deque();\n\n        function addDeque(element) {\n            deque.push(element);\n        }\n\n        function printDeque() {\n            console.log(\"Deque:\", deque);\n        }\n\n        function removeDeque() {\n            console.log(\"Deque:\", deque.pop());\n        }\n\n        function clearDeque() {\n            deque.clear();\n        }\n\n        function insertAtFront(element) {\n            deque.push(element);\n        }\n\n        function insertAtBack(element) {\n            deque.push(element);\n        }\n\n        function removeFromFront() {\n            console.log(\"Deque:\", deque.shift());\n        }\n\n        function removeFromBack() {\n            console.log(\"Deque:\", deque.pop());\n        }\n\n        function getSize() {\n            console.log(\"Deque size:\", deque.size);\n        }\n\n        function getFront() {\n            console.log(\"Front element:\", deque.front);\n        }\n\n        function getBack() {\n            console.log(\"Back element:\", deque.back);\n        }\n\n        function peek() {\n            console.log(\"Peek:\", deque.peek());\n        }\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"
